<br>
All we can do is give examples of what exploits are and make our own definition of it.<br>
<br>
Examples of exploits:<br>
<br>
1: Using pathing to take no or little damage while you kill a mob.<br>
<br>
2:  Using the Z axis to pull a mob to make it warp without having to fight to it.<br>
<br>
3: Killing Traders in the Bazaar<br>
<br>
4:  Players crashing a zone, as this pops up from time to time with different patches.<br>
<br>
Those are the only major ones I can think of at the moment.  Basically it is using a little common sense.<br>
<br>
Feel Free to add more to this list.  <br>
