<br>
A bit of an unlikely conspiracy theory perhaps but the point remains that before we can debate whether this is an exploit or not we need to know whether Sony intended this effect. As I said above we cannot know this so we cannot judge whether it is an exploit or not. And this is pretty much the case with ANY possible exploit.<br>
